find authors:

findAuthors.php scans the folder of extracted pdf text and generates a number of files with recognised entities using the opencalais API. the most important file is 'names.json' but there are some other formats of the same info generated for Ahren Warner. Also generated is a list of the most popular found enities in order 'popularity.txt'

